==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Botox'''&trade;

# a [[toxic]] [[compound]], ([[generic]] name ''botulinum toxin type A''), produced by the [[bacterium]] ''[[Clostridium botulinum]]'', that causes the [[paralysis]] of [[muscle]]s
# some [[off label]], non-toxic uses include:  [[cosmetic surgery]] to [[conceal]] [[wrinkle]]s, muscle spasm relief and headache prevention

